{"id":585670,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【立此存照】天降伟人-买三赠一（附近日习近平相/","date":"2018-05-29T07:00:56Z","modified":"2018-05-29T09:43:31Z","title":"【立此存照】天降伟人  买三赠一（附近日习近平相关审查三例）","content":"<p>BBC 驻华记者 Stephen McDonell (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StephenMcDonell\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@StephenMcDonell</a>) 近日在香港机场发现，某书店正在进行“买三赠一”的促销，而《习近平谈治国理政》第二卷也赫然出现在了促销架上：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeSg_aFVwAAoIF6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585664\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeSg_aFVwAAoIF6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeSg_aFVwAAoIF6.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeSg_aFVwAAoIF6-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeSg_aFVwAAoIF6-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeSg_aFVwAAoIF6-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Saw this in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKong</a> Airport: buy 3 get 1 free!!! &#8230;What a bargain!!!<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/China?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#China</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/w6AGDx7Guo\">pic.twitter.com/w6AGDx7Guo</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Stephen McDonell (@StephenMcDonell) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/StephenMcDonell/status/1001102044764127232?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 28, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>附：近日习近平相关审查三例</strong></p>\n<h3>1.</h3>\n<p>2018年5月27日，任贤齐在微博给增肥后的自己配了一张与小熊维尼的对比图，相关评论和转发内容很快遭到屏蔽。截至发稿时，该微博已被删除：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeMznAFXUAI7JfV.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585663\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeMznAFXUAI7JfV.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeMznAFXUAI7JfV.jpg 928w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeMznAFXUAI7JfV-232x300.jpg 232w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeMznAFXUAI7JfV-768x993.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DeMznAFXUAI7JfV-792x1024.jpg 792w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">任贤齐可能是第一个不知道为什么被屏蔽的明星。 <a href=\"https://t.co/fG4ymdERCH\">pic.twitter.com/fG4ymdERCH</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 🐳 (@Uromayutori) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Uromayutori/status/1000700294198644736?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 27, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<h3>2.</h3>\n<p>2018年5月26日，自媒体账号 @生活大爆炸TBBT 在微博发布了一则真人版小熊维尼电影预告片，评论和转发内容因为充满调侃和隐喻，很快遭到屏蔽：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_585665\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/真人版维尼.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-585665\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/真人版维尼.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"621\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/真人版维尼.jpg 910w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/真人版维尼-242x300.jpg 242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/真人版维尼-768x954.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/真人版维尼-825x1024.jpg 825w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<h3>3.</h3>\n<p>2018年5月23日，华创证券2018年中期策略会某场演讲的大屏幕上赫然出现了《苹果日报》制作的讽刺习近平的图片。在网络引来热传并遭删除后，华创证券发布公告（<a href=\"http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:jxl00RODTrMJ:stock.qq.com/a/20180523/023251.htm+\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">谷歌快照</a>），称这张图片是“外籍专家发表《美国对华政策的四股潮流及其成因》演讲时，批判当前西方对中国的错误思潮时引用的海外媒体图片，并非其本人原创”，并强调该专家“意在批评西方媒体对中国的错误认知”。相关公告随后在网络遭到全面封杀。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_585452\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/Dd8OgX9UwAAbzDy.jpg-large.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-585452\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/Dd8OgX9UwAAbzDy.jpg-large.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/Dd8OgX9UwAAbzDy.jpg-large.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/Dd8OgX9UwAAbzDy.jpg-large-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/Dd8OgX9UwAAbzDy.jpg-large-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">从现场照片中甚至可以看出图片右下角的《苹果日报》水印；网络图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_585667\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/华创证券.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-585667\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/华创证券.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/华创证券.jpg 1670w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/华创证券-300x188.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/华创证券-768x481.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/华创证券-1024x641.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">被删报道谷歌快照截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[25995,32609,25917]}